"Extend your Google Sheets integration with powerful add-ons. Install, manage, and "
"activate extensions to unlock advanced features."
msgstr ""
"Breid je Google Sheets-integratie uit met krachtige add-ons. Installeer, beheer "
"en activeer extensies om geavanceerde functies te ontgrendelen."

msgid ""
"Easily connect Contact Form 7 to Google Sheets and automatically sync form "
"submissions in real-time. Every entry is instantly added to your selected "
"spreadsheet, helping you manage leads, inquiries, and customer data efficiently "
"without manual export."
msgstr ""
"Verbind Contact Form 7 eenvoudig met Google Sheets en synchroniseer "
"formulierinzendingen automatisch in realtime. Elke invoer wordt direct aan je "
"geselecteerde spreadsheet toegevoegd, zodat je leads, aanvragen en klantgegevens "
"efficiënt kunt beheren zonder handmatige export."

msgid "Install"
msgstr "Installeren"

msgid ""
"Integrate WPForms with Google Sheets and send form entries directly to your "
"spreadsheet automatically. Track leads, manage customer data, and streamline "
"reporting with seamless Google Sheets integration and real-time sync."
msgstr ""
"Integreer WPForms met Google Sheets en stuur formulierinvoeren automatisch direct "
"naar je spreadsheet. Volg leads, beheer klantgegevens en stroomlijn rapportage "
"met naadloze Google Sheets-integratie en realtime synchronisatie."

msgid ""
"Connect Gravity Forms to Google Sheets and automatically push form submissions to "
"your spreadsheet. Simplify data management, improve workflow automation, and keep "
"all entries organized in one secure location."
msgstr ""
"Verbind Gravity Forms met Google Sheets en duw formulierinzendingen automatisch "
"naar je spreadsheet. Vereenvoudig gegevensbeheer, verbeter workflowautomatisering "
"en houd alle invoeren georganiseerd op één veilige locatie."

msgid ""
"Automatically sync Ninja Forms submissions to Google Sheets with one-click "
"integration. Capture leads, monitor responses, and manage data efficiently with "
"instant spreadsheet updates and easy reporting."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer automatisch Ninja Forms-inzendingen met Google Sheets met een klik-"
"integratie. Leg leads vast, monitor reacties en beheer gegevens efficiënt met "
"directe spreadsheet-updates en eenvoudige rapportage."

msgid ""
"Integrate Forminator Forms with Google Sheets to automatically store form entries "
"in your spreadsheet. Eliminate manual data entry and ensure accurate, real-time "
"syncing for better data tracking and analysis."
msgstr ""
"Integreer Forminator Forms met Google Sheets om formulierinvoeren automatisch in "
"je spreadsheet op te slaan. Elimineer handmatige gegevensinvoer en zorg voor "
"nauwkeurige, realtime synchronisatie voor betere gegevensregistratie en analyse."

msgid "Free"
msgstr "Gratis"

msgid ""
"Automatically sync Formidable Forms entries to Google Sheets. Manage leads, track "
"submissions, and simplify data reporting with real-time integration."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer automatisch Formidable Forms inzendingen met Google Sheets. Beheer "
"leads, volg inzendingen en vereenvoudig datarapportage met realtime integratie."

msgid ""
"Automatically sync Fluent Forms submissions to Google Sheets in real-time. Every "
"form entry is instantly added to your selected spreadsheet, helping you manage "
"leads, customer inquiries, and business data without manual export. Streamline "
"your workflow, improve reporting accuracy, and keep all submissions organized "
"with seamless Google Sheets integration."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer automatisch Fluent Forms-indieningen in realtime met Google Sheets. "
"Elke formulierinvoer wordt onmiddellijk toegevoegd aan je geselecteerde "
"spreadsheet, waardoor je leads, klantvragen en bedrijfsgegevens zonder handmatige "
"export kunt beheren. Stroomlijn je workflow, verbeter de nauwkeurigheid van "
"rapportages en houd alle indieningen georganiseerd met naadloze Google Sheets-"
"integratie."

msgid ""
"Sync Elementor Forms with Google Sheets instantly. Automatically add new form "
"submissions to your spreadsheet, manage leads efficiently, and simplify reporting "
"with real-time data synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer Elementor Forms direct met Google Sheets. Voeg automatisch nieuwe "
"formulierinzendingen toe aan je spreadsheet, beheer leads efficiënt en "
"vereenvoudig rapportage met realtime datasychronisatie."

msgid ""
"Connect Avada Forms to Google Sheets and automatically transfer form entries to "
"your spreadsheet. Streamline lead management, automate data collection, and "
"improve business reporting with seamless integration."
msgstr ""
"Verbind Avada Forms met Google Sheets en verzend automatisch formulierinzendingen "
"naar je spreadsheet. Stroomlijn leadbeheer, automatiseer gegevensverzameling en "
"verbeter bedrijfsrapportage met naadloze integratie."

msgid "Available PRO Version"
msgstr "Beschikbare PRO Versie"

msgid ""
"Integrate Divi Forms with Google Sheets and automatically sync submissions in "
"real-time. Store customer data securely, track inquiries efficiently, and "
"eliminate manual spreadsheet updates."
msgstr ""
"Integreer Divi Forms met Google Sheets en synchroniseer inzendingen automatisch "
"in realtime. Bewaar klantgegevens veilig, volg aanvragen efficiënt en elimineer "
"handmatige spreadsheetupdates."

msgid ""
"Automatically send WordPress core data (like comments or custom submissions) to "
"Google Sheets. Simplify website data tracking, automate record keeping, and "
"centralize important information in one organized spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Verzend automatisch WordPress kerngegevens (zoals opmerkingen of aangepaste "
"inzendingen) naar Google Sheets. Vereenvoudig websitegegevenstracking, "
"automatiseer het bijhouden van gegevens en centraliseer belangrijke informatie in "
"één georganiseerde spreadsheet."

msgid ""
"Sync WooCommerce orders with Google Sheets automatically. Store order details, "
"customer information, and transaction data in real-time for easy reporting, "
"accounting, and business analysis."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer WooCommerce bestellingen automatisch met Google Sheets. Bewaar "
"bestelgegevens, klantinformatie en transactiegegevens in realtime voor eenvoudige "
"rapportage, boekhouding en bedrijfsanalyse."

msgid ""
"Automatically send Easy Digital Downloads (EDD) order details to Google Sheets. "
"Track digital product sales, monitor transactions, and manage customer data "
"effortlessly with real-time spreadsheet integration."
msgstr ""
"Verzend automatisch Easy Digital Downloads (EDD) bestelgegevens naar Google "
"Sheets. Volg digitale productverkopen, monitor transacties en beheer "
"klantgegevens moeiteloos met realtime spreadsheetintegratie."

